KSLawdogg, Ramulus and Spears were in North America, several thousand miles 
away from Serpentor and Striker, who were somewhere in Africa.

::Ramulus::

Ramulus looks at surprise from Spears to Striker, who had magically 
teleported along with Serpentor (I guess).

"Am I allright?" he says as Striker lands near the two, "I'm perfectly fine, 
but you need a CR chamber."

Striker sighs. "I can fly her there if you want, I need one too."

Ramulus nods, looking at Spears. "Do you want to go with Striker? He'll take 
you back to the base."
